divs: Sighting Detailsi was out in my back yard at around 10pm i always look up in the sky looking for objects this time i saw one. i notice bright light coming up in the west over another house and i thought it was a plane or jet or helicopter spot light i watched it rise in the sky and fly over head it never lost its brightness no matter where it was in the sky it had no flashing lights and it didnt make a sound it flew in a sraight line i watch it until it disappeared over to the east it looked like a big spot light in the sky but it radiated white light in all directions no matter where it was in the sky i kept checking the sky to see if i could have mistaken it for a jet but i saw jets up in the sky they all had flashing marker lights and i could here them i feel i saw something that could be a ufo im feeling excited and im going back to see if i can spot it again
